Function description: During the navigation process of the robot, the corner point of the path is an important factor affecting the motion state. In order to obtain better wall-mounting performance, the robot will strictly reach the corner point and rotate in place and continue to drive. If you do not need to strictly follow the line or pay for money during driving, you can also skip the corner point and directly track the subsequent path near the corner point. The parameter of the switching mode is (strategy.yaml) movebase: shortcut_corner. In addition, in shortcut corner mode, when the distance from the corner sentence is less than the specified range, the system will slow down.

Function description: In navigation mode, after entering the planning or control failure recovery mode, the timeout time will be accumulated. The timeout time is related to the task type. If the task is navigation, the parameter is goal_base:planner_error_patience_time. If it is obstacle avoidance or offroad in follow-up mode, the parameter is goal_base:follow_path_patience_time; the timeout time of failure to obtain the target point is controlled by goal_base:avoid_goal_obstacle_stop_duration.
